This beginner-friendly machine learning project uses the historical Titanic dataset to predict whether a passenger survived the tragic sinking of the RMS Titanic. By analyzing features like age, gender, ticket class, and fare, the model uncovers patterns in survival and explores the impact of socio-economic factors.
